column5: These two rods are for a client in Manitoba, where they tell me the wind chill is -40. I took these pictures this afternoon, when the wind chill was +75F. I hope you-guys are staying warm and dry. Garry2R's.      Detail of Harley-Davidson theme and Tiger-wrap..    Detail of Giants theme and Tiger-wrap...
Nice job on the tiger and labels.     What does it say on the spinning rod just behind the foregrip?
Although that type of graphic on fishing rods doesn't appeal to me personally, it's excellent work!  Very cool, thanks
Very good work again Garry! I hope you're saving some blanks for yourself
